T-Shirts for Women: Cropped, Classic, & Oversized

Go beyond basic with our women’s t-shirts at American Eagle. We make ‘em in the best colors and softest fabrics so you can improve your tried and true jeans and a t-shirt vibe. Upgrade your style with our extensive line of long sleeve t-shirts, short sleeve t-shirts, polo shirts & more. With all the fits, colors & designs you can think of, AE t-shirts have got you covered for all your women’s shirts & tops needs. Find your new favorite cropped shirt, oversized shirt, and classic fitting t-shirt only at American Eagle. Think outside the box and make all your layering dreams come true starting with these tees.

If your outfit of the day calls for a solid base layer then suit up with our plain t-shirts. Long sleeve styles look good under your favorite denim jackets, and short sleeve shirts are just right when worn under flannels and sweaters. AE women’s t-shirts are available in scoop neck, mock neck, crew neck and V-neck styles, and come in a variety of hues that go with everything in your closet! Dress them up for your next date with a high-waisted skirt and heels or go for a casual look that’s perfect for class or coffee by teaming them with your favorite women’s jeans and booties.

Our Women’s T-shirts are on trend for every season. From striped designs to bold graphics, bright colors to more laid-back hues, we’ve got it all. We make them in form-fitting styles and more drapey fits so you can have the look you want. Pair a relaxed graphic tee with a high-waisted jean for a throwback vibe, or pair a fitted long sleeve shirt with a button front skirt for a look that’s good for the office and for drinks after work with friends. And if you’re looking for a preppier option, try one of our women’s polo shirts. Bold stripes and tipping add a fresh touch to these iconic staples that we love wearing with all the best AE jeans.

Whatever the weather, whatever the season, whatever the outfit… AE women’s tops & shirts have got all the fits you need to get the job done. Update your women’s t-shirt vibe with a little help from AE, and stock up on fall and winter faves like flannel shirts, jean jackets, Sherpa sweatshirts & hoodies, puffer coats, oversized sweaters, and every other cold-weather essential you can think of. Layer them with your new t-shirts and you're set with a classic style that looks as good as it feels every time you wear it.
